## 🔄 데이터 흐름

### INSERT 요청
```
1. Client
   ↓
2. Coordinator.routeInsertRequest(vectorId, vector)
   ├─ ShardRouter.getPartitionId(vectorId) → partition 0-15
   ├─ ShardRouter.getReplicaNodes(partition) → [n1, n2, n3]
   ↓
3. ReplicationManager.quorumWrite(req, cluster)
   ├─ RaftIndexNode(n1).appendVectorCommand() [Leader]
   ├─ RaftIndexNode(n2).appendVectorCommand() [Replica]
   └─ RaftIndexNode(n3).appendVectorCommand() [Replica]
   ↓
4. updateCommitIndex() → 2/3 성공 확인
   ↓
5. applyCommittedCommands()
   ↓
6. RaftIndexNode.applyVectorCommand(cmd)
   ├─ cmd.commandType == "INSERT"
   ├─ vector = deserialize(cmd.payload)
   ↓
7. HybridIndex.hybridInsert(vector) ← ★ 핵심 통합점
   ├─ vectorInsert() [정확한 일치]
   ├─ approximateInsert() [근사 검색]
   └─ updateMetadata()
   ↓
8. Response: Ok(quorumResult)
```

### SEARCH 요청
```
1. Client: query vector, topK=10
   ↓
2. Coordinator.routeSearchRequest(query, topK)
   ├─ ShardRouter.getPartitionIds() → [0..15]
   ↓
3. Parallel search on all 16 partitions
   ├─ RaftIndexNode(n1).HybridIndex.hybridSearch(query, topK) → [10 결과]
   ├─ RaftIndexNode(n2).HybridIndex.hybridSearch(query, topK) → [10 결과]
   ├─ ...
   └─ RaftIndexNode(n16).HybridIndex.hybridSearch(query, topK) → [10 결과]
   ↓
4. aggregateSearchResults(partialResults[], topK=10)
   ├─ merge(16 × 10 = 160 결과)
   ├─ sortByScoredVectors(내림차순)
   └─ return Top-10 ← ★ 글로벌 Top-K
   ↓
5. Response: [top10 ScoredVector]
```

### FAILOVER 시나리오
```
1. Heartbeat timeout: 3 periods (450ms default)
   ↓
2. Coordinator.monitorHeartbeats(currentTimeMs)
   ├─ timeSinceHeartbeat > deadTimeoutMs
   ↓
3. Coordinator.markNodeDead(nodeId, cluster)
   ├─ node.state = "DEAD"
   ├─ removeNodeFromRing()
   ↓
4. ReplicationManager.detectNodeFailure(nodeId, cluster)
   ├─ affectedPartitions = [p1, p2, p3, ...] (노드가 primary인 파티션)
   ↓
5. ReplicationManager.initiateFailover()
   ├─ selectReplacementNode(failedId, candidates) → newPrimary
   ├─ promoteReplica(partitionId, newPrimary)
   │  └─ ReplicaSet.primaryNodeId = newPrimary
   ↓
6. 이후 INSERT/SEARCH: 새 Primary로 라우팅
```

